author: jork
description: A collection of custom utility classes designed to standardize and simplify common tasks for jork's OSMB scripts.

utilities.description: Consistent logging helpers with global log-level filtering and script-friendly formatting.

methods.name: setMinLevel
methods.description: Sets the global minimum log level; messages below this are suppressed.

methods.name: setDebugEnabled
methods.description: Convenience toggle for enabling or disabling debug logging.

methods.name: info
methods.description: Logs a standard informational message.

methods.name: warning
methods.description: Logs a warning message for recoverable errors.

methods.name: error
methods.description: Logs a critical error message.

methods.name: debug
methods.description: Logs a verbose debug message.

methods.name: actionAttempt
methods.description: Logs an action attempt for standardized flow tracing.

methods.name: actionSuccess
methods.description: Logs a successful action.

methods.name: actionFailure
methods.description: Logs a failed action with retry info.

methods.name: stateChange
methods.description: Logs a state transition with optional reason.

methods.name: inventoryStatus
methods.description: Logs inventory snapshot as name/count pairs.

methods.name: exception
methods.description: Logs exception details with stack trace at debug level.

utilities.description: Exception helpers to ensure TaskInterruptedException propagates correctly.

methods.name: rethrowIfTaskInterrupted
methods.description: Rethrows TaskInterruptedException if present in the cause chain.

utilities.description: Draws debug markers on screen for z-offset calibration.

methods.name: drawZOffsetMarker
methods.description: Draws a 3x3 marker at a projected tile point for a given z-offset.

utilities.description: Banking helper with verified open/deposit/withdraw operations and explicit result enums.

constructor.description: Creates a new JorkBank tied to a script.

methods.name: open
methods.description: Opens nearest bank; optionally accepts a custom object filter.

methods.name: close
methods.description: Closes bank interface if open.

methods.name: deposit
methods.description: Deposits items by id (amount or all).

methods.name: depositAllExcept
methods.description: Deposits all inventory items except listed IDs.

methods.name: withdraw
methods.description: Withdraws items from bank into inventory.

methods.name: contains
methods.description: Checks bank for item count.

methods.name: getCount
methods.description: Gets the count of a specific item in the bank.

methods.name: isBankNearby
methods.description: Detects reachable bank objects within distance.

utilities.description: Navigation helper that wraps walking, obstacle handling, and short-range screen taps.

constructor.description: Creates a new Navigation instance tied to a script.

components.name: Obstacle
components.description: Defines script-specific obstacles that should be handled while walking.

methods.name: getArea
methods.description: Area of the obstacle.

methods.name: needsHandling
methods.description: Whether the obstacle needs interaction.

methods.name: handle
methods.description: Performs the interaction.

methods.name: navigateTo
methods.description: Navigates to an area using optional WalkConfig, obstacles, and break conditions.
overloads: navigateTo(Area destination, List<Obstacle> obstacles, BooleanSupplier breakCondition, int timeout, WalkConfig.Builder builder)

methods.name: simpleMoveTo
methods.description: Short-range movement via screen tap with walker fallback.
overloads: simpleMoveTo(WorldPosition targetPosition, int timeout, int tolerance)

utilities.description: Tap spamming helpers for shapes, areas, and world positions with optional human delay.

methods.name: spamTap
methods.description: Repeatedly taps a screen-space shape until condition or max taps.
overloads: spamTap(Script script, Shape shape, int minDelayMs, int maxDelayMs, int maxTaps, BooleanSupplier condition)
spamTap(Script script, Shape shape, int minDelayMs, int maxDelayMs, int maxTaps, BooleanSupplier condition, boolean human)

methods.name: spamTapArea
methods.description: Repeatedly taps a world-space RectangleArea.
overloads: spamTapArea(Script script, RectangleArea area, int cubeHeight, int minDelayMs, int maxDelayMs, int maxTaps, BooleanSupplier condition)
spamTapArea(Script script, RectangleArea area, int cubeHeight, int minDelayMs, int maxDelayMs, int maxTaps, BooleanSupplier condition, boolean human)

methods.name: spamTapPosition
methods.description: Repeatedly taps a world position projected to screen.
overloads: spamTapPosition(Script script, WorldPosition position, int cubeHeight, int minDelayMs, int maxDelayMs, int maxTaps, BooleanSupplier condition)
spamTapPosition(Script script, WorldPosition position, int cubeHeight, int minDelayMs, int maxDelayMs, int maxTaps, BooleanSupplier condition, boolean human)

methods.name: convertAreaToPolygon
methods.description: Projects a RectangleArea to a screen-space polygon.

methods.name: convertPositionToPolygon
methods.description: Projects a WorldPosition to a screen-space polygon.

utilities.description: Simple JavaFX panel to select a single tile on screen.

methods.name: show
methods.description: Shows the panel and returns the selected WorldPosition.

utilities.description: Multi-select tile picker with optional categories and builder configuration.

methods.name: show
methods.description: Backwards-compatible single tile selection.

methods.name: showMultiple
methods.description: Multi-select without categories, returns list of positions.

methods.name: showWithCategories
methods.description: Multi-select with categories, returns map of category id to positions.

methods.name: builder
methods.description: Builder entrypoint for custom configuration.

utilities.description: Defines a tile category with id, display name, color, and optional selection limit.
Represents a selected tile and its category id.

Represents a registered chat handler with naming, trigger counts, and removal.

constructor.description: Creates a listener for the given script.

methods.name: on
methods.description: Registers a handler for matching messages.

methods.name: onOnce
methods.description: Registers a one-time handler.

methods.name: onTimes
methods.description: Registers a handler with a max trigger count.

methods.name: monitorTabs
methods.description: Allows monitoring multiple chat tabs.

methods.name: setAutoSwitchToTab
methods.description: Auto-switches to a specific chat tab on update.

methods.name: update
methods.description: Processes new chatbox lines and triggers handlers.

methods.name: remove
methods.description: Removes a handler by name or reference.

utilities.description: Base script class that initializes and renders the metrics system.

registerMetric(String label, Supplier<Object> valueSupplier, MetricType type, String format)
